1
00:00:01,001 --> 00:00:04,170
<i>Tell us, did you and</i>
<i>Louisa have a relationship?</i>

2
00:00:05,380 --> 00:00:06,339
<i>I'm Bana.</i>

3
00:00:06,423 --> 00:00:08,508
<i>Louisa and I were</i>
<i>in a relationship before.</i>

4
00:00:08,591 --> 00:00:10,135
<i>I loved Louisa.</i>

5
00:00:10,218 --> 00:00:12,220
<i>We loved each other.</i>

6
00:00:12,762 --> 00:00:15,640
<i>When I'm with you, I'm happy.</i>

7
00:00:15,724 --> 00:00:18,768
<i>I wish I could be with you all the time.</i>

8
00:00:19,185 --> 00:00:21,229
<i>Ever since you saw who I really am.</i>

9
00:00:21,771 --> 00:00:23,148
<i>Liezel, I like you.</i>

10
00:00:24,315 --> 00:00:25,483
<i>I love you, Liezel.</i>

11
00:00:25,567 --> 00:00:30,280
["Nagmamahal Lang Ako"
by KZ Tandingan playing]

12
00:00:37,037 --> 00:00:43,752
[theme music playing]

13
00:01:53,279 --> 00:01:54,531
<i>Careful.</i>

14
00:01:54,614 --> 00:01:57,075
<i>Where are we going? </i>[giggles]

15
00:01:57,158 --> 00:01:59,494
<i>Just wait, we're almost there.</i>

16
00:02:02,831 --> 00:02:04,207
<i>Surprise!</i>

17
00:02:04,290 --> 00:02:05,458
[Louisa giggles]

18
00:02:06,084 --> 00:02:09,879
[gentle music playing]

19
00:02:09,963 --> 00:02:10,964
[Louisa] <i>Do you like it?</i>

20
00:02:13,925 --> 00:02:18,138
[gentle music continues]

21
00:02:19,556 --> 00:02:21,141
<i>How did you find this place?</i>

22
00:02:21,599 --> 00:02:24,269
<i>I saw it when I was walking around.</i>

23
00:02:24,978 --> 00:02:28,606
<i>I come here when I want to be alone.</i>

24
00:02:29,607 --> 00:02:32,819
<i>Because sometimes,</i>
<i>everything's just too loud.</i>

25
00:02:34,028 --> 00:02:36,865
<i>And my brothers aren't helping at all.</i>

26
00:02:40,118 --> 00:02:42,704
<i>Some people are scared to come here.</i>

27
00:02:44,205 --> 00:02:47,542
<i>But when I'm here,</i>

28
00:02:48,710 --> 00:02:50,628
<i>all the noise disappears.</i>

29
00:02:53,381 --> 00:02:57,719
[gentle music continues]

30
00:03:01,681 --> 00:03:03,474
<i>We can make this our place.</i>

31
00:03:04,934 --> 00:03:05,935
<i>Our place?</i>

32
00:03:07,061 --> 00:03:08,062
<i>Hm.</i>

33
00:03:08,646 --> 00:03:10,148
<i>Nobody else comes here.</i>

34
00:03:13,568 --> 00:03:17,780
<i>Here, I can be your Bana.</i>

35
00:03:17,864 --> 00:03:18,907
<i>Huh?</i>

36
00:03:19,365 --> 00:03:21,200
<i>I'm supposed to be your Bana.</i>

37
00:03:22,035 --> 00:03:24,078
[in Bisaya] <i>I'm your Bana.</i>

38
00:03:24,162 --> 00:03:25,580
<i>I'm the Bana.</i>

39
00:03:25,663 --> 00:03:27,165
[both giggling]

40
00:03:27,248 --> 00:03:28,708
<i>Yeah, I remember.</i>

41
00:03:30,835 --> 00:03:32,003
[sighs]

42
00:03:34,464 --> 00:03:36,341
<i>We're each other's Bana.</i>

43
00:03:37,842 --> 00:03:39,344
<i>Wait, I'll show you something.</i>

44
00:03:39,427 --> 00:03:41,137
<i>Let's go! Be careful.</i>

45
00:03:41,888 --> 00:03:43,056
<i>Come here.</i>

46
00:03:44,891 --> 00:03:46,226
<i>- Go on, sit.</i>
<i>- Oh.</i>

47
00:03:48,436 --> 00:03:50,146
[giggles]

48
00:03:50,230 --> 00:03:51,272
<i>Come on.</i>

49
00:03:51,356 --> 00:03:53,316
<i>- Sit with me.</i>
<i>- We don't fit there.</i>

50
00:03:53,399 --> 00:03:54,651
<i>We do. Sit here.</i>

51
00:03:54,734 --> 00:03:56,444
<i>Don't blame me if it breaks.</i>

52
00:03:56,945 --> 00:03:58,363
[Louisa chuckles]

53
00:03:58,446 --> 00:04:02,283
[gentle music continues]

54
00:04:10,416 --> 00:04:12,919
[Liezel] We couldn't even walk together.

55
00:04:13,378 --> 00:04:15,672
In front of the whole world.

56
00:04:15,755 --> 00:04:17,632
[sobs]

57
00:04:17,715 --> 00:04:21,469
[music becomes somber]

58
00:04:29,143 --> 00:04:32,146
[Louisa] <i>Careful, okay? You might trip.</i>
<i>You might fall for me.</i>

59
00:04:32,647 --> 00:04:34,732
<i>Hmm. I already fell for you.</i>

60
00:04:37,277 --> 00:04:38,945
<i>- You flirt!</i>
- [Liezel chuckles]

61
00:04:39,028 --> 00:04:40,655
<i>Oh, you're fighting back?</i>

62
00:04:40,738 --> 00:04:41,864
[both giggling]

63
00:04:42,699 --> 00:04:44,784
<i>Why, is it not true?</i>

64
00:04:44,867 --> 00:04:47,829
[both giggling]

65
00:04:47,912 --> 00:04:50,790
[gentle music resumes]

66
00:04:51,249 --> 00:04:52,166
<i>What?</i>

67
00:04:56,170 --> 00:04:57,338
<i>Surprise!</i>

68
00:04:59,882 --> 00:05:05,138
["Nagmamahal Lang Ako"
by KZ Tandingan playing]

69
00:05:12,729 --> 00:05:13,896
<i>"L"?</i>

70
00:05:16,774 --> 00:05:18,526
<i>"L" for…</i>

71
00:05:18,609 --> 00:05:19,736
<i>love?</i>

72
00:05:21,321 --> 00:05:22,905
<i>It's you…</i>

73
00:05:22,989 --> 00:05:24,782
<i>and only you I'll choose.</i>

74
00:05:26,492 --> 00:05:27,660
<i>Again and again.</i>

75
00:05:36,878 --> 00:05:41,049
["Nagmamahal Lang Ako" continues]

76
00:05:50,516 --> 00:05:51,684
<i>Again and again.</i>

77
00:05:55,688 --> 00:06:00,943
["Nagmamahal Lang Ako" continues]

78
00:06:06,115 --> 00:06:09,744
I couldn't even tell
the world that she's the one I love!

79
00:06:09,827 --> 00:06:13,998
[somber music playing]

80
00:06:22,048 --> 00:06:23,841
[student 1] <i>This one eats so much!</i>

81
00:06:23,925 --> 00:06:27,095
- [student 1] <i>Don't do that!</i>
- [student 2] <i>How much I owe?</i>

82
00:06:27,178 --> 00:06:29,180
- [student 3] <i>When will you pay?</i>
<i>- Hold on…</i>

83
00:06:29,263 --> 00:06:31,808
<i>- How many buns do you want?</i>
<i>- Hey! I told you earlier!</i>

84
00:06:31,891 --> 00:06:34,685
<i>Even if it's just one pork bun,</i>
<i>as long as there's love in it.</i>

85
00:06:34,769 --> 00:06:37,355
<i>- Then give it to her!</i>
- [student 2] <i>Give it to her!</i>

86
00:06:37,438 --> 00:06:40,191
- [student 3] <i>Do it now!</i>
- [student 1]<i> Look at Beth!</i>

87
00:06:40,274 --> 00:06:41,901
<i>- She's so beautiful!</i>
<i>- Give it to her, bro!</i>

88
00:06:41,984 --> 00:06:43,319
- [student 1] <i>Give it.</i>
<i>- Go!</i>

89
00:06:43,402 --> 00:06:45,154
- [student 2] <i>Go talk to her!</i>
<i>- Fine.</i>

90
00:06:45,238 --> 00:06:47,782
<i>- There he is!</i>
- [giggling]

91
00:06:47,865 --> 00:06:49,992
<i>- Beth, look!</i>
<i>- Look!</i>

92
00:06:50,076 --> 00:06:50,993
<i>He has something for you.</i>

93
00:06:51,077 --> 00:06:52,203
<i>- Here he comes!</i>
- [squealing]

94
00:06:52,286 --> 00:06:53,663
<i>Go, Prince Joey!</i>

95
00:06:53,746 --> 00:06:55,289
[young Beth] <i>It's bad to assume!</i>

96
00:06:55,373 --> 00:06:56,374
<i>There he goes.</i>

97
00:06:56,457 --> 00:06:58,042
<i>- That's my man!</i>
- [squealing]

98
00:06:58,126 --> 00:07:01,087
[somber music playing]

99
00:07:01,170 --> 00:07:03,005
<i>- Beth?</i>
<i>- Hmm?</i>

100
00:07:03,089 --> 00:07:04,674
<i>Pork buns for you.</i>

101
00:07:04,757 --> 00:07:05,633
<i>That's for you, girl.</i>

102
00:07:05,716 --> 00:07:07,009
<i>Go away!</i>

103
00:07:07,093 --> 00:07:09,137
[squealing]

104
00:07:09,220 --> 00:07:11,264
<i>- That's sweet!</i>
<i>- Go ahead, eat it!</i>

105
00:07:11,347 --> 00:07:12,682
<i>He went all the way here for that!</i>

106
00:07:12,765 --> 00:07:14,600
<i>- Come on, don't waste it!</i>
<i>- Here, eat it!</i>

107
00:07:14,684 --> 00:07:16,227
[young Beth] <i>I don't want it. I'm full.</i>

108
00:07:16,310 --> 00:07:18,104
<i>- I already ate.</i>
<i>- He made an effort for that!</i>

109
00:07:18,187 --> 00:07:19,147
<i>Well, I didn't say…</i>

110
00:07:19,230 --> 00:07:20,940
[Liezel] She couldn't admit to everyone

111
00:07:21,524 --> 00:07:23,151
that I'm the one she loves.

112
00:07:23,234 --> 00:07:27,488
[somber music continues]

113
00:07:35,288 --> 00:07:36,789
<i>Are you mad at me?</i>

114
00:07:37,582 --> 00:07:40,543
<i>Because you can't tell people about us?</i>

115
00:07:41,127 --> 00:07:42,503
<i>Not even your friends?</i>

116
00:07:44,130 --> 00:07:50,678
<i>I want to tell Erica,</i>
<i>Mel, Alice, and Beth, but…</i>

117
00:07:53,347 --> 00:07:56,309
<i>I get it. You're just scared of your dad.</i>

118
00:07:57,477 --> 00:07:59,145
<i>He'll separate us.</i>

119
00:07:59,228 --> 00:08:01,647
[pensive music playing]

120
00:08:01,731 --> 00:08:03,774
<i>Is it a problem for you,</i>

121
00:08:04,692 --> 00:08:08,279
<i>that only we know we love each other?</i>

122
00:08:09,405 --> 00:08:10,323
[sighs deeply]

123
00:08:10,406 --> 00:08:15,203
[pensive music continues]

124
00:08:15,286 --> 00:08:16,954
[exhales sharply] <i>No.</i>

125
00:08:20,458 --> 00:08:22,793
<i>You're the only one who matters to me.</i>

126
00:08:22,877 --> 00:08:25,421
[pensive music continues]

127
00:08:25,505 --> 00:08:27,006
[Liezel] That's what we said.

128
00:08:28,799 --> 00:08:29,800
[Liezel sobs]

129
00:08:30,551 --> 00:08:33,054
It's easy to say…

130
00:08:33,137 --> 00:08:36,891
[pensive music continues]

131
00:08:43,773 --> 00:08:45,149
but hard to face.

132
00:08:48,694 --> 00:08:50,112
[music fades]

133
00:08:50,196 --> 00:08:51,364
<i>- Hey!</i>
<i>- I missed you.</i>

134
00:08:51,447 --> 00:08:53,574
<i>Hey, my dad might see us.</i>

135
00:08:53,658 --> 00:08:55,493
<i>Come on, I just missed you.</i>

136
00:08:56,285 --> 00:08:57,286
<i>Oh.</i>

137
00:08:58,454 --> 00:09:00,414
<i>Your birthday's coming up, right?</i>

138
00:09:00,915 --> 00:09:01,916
<i>What's our plan?</i>

139
00:09:03,876 --> 00:09:05,920
<i>My dad has a charity event on that day.</i>

140
00:09:06,003 --> 00:09:07,255
<i>I'll help.</i>

141
00:09:07,338 --> 00:09:08,881
<i>It's in the next town.</i>

142
00:09:09,423 --> 00:09:11,634
<i>He always does that on my birthday.</i>

143
00:09:12,802 --> 00:09:17,223
<i>He said instead of celebrating,</i>
<i>we should just help others.</i>

144
00:09:18,266 --> 00:09:20,309
<i>It's usually the whole day.</i>

145
00:09:21,894 --> 00:09:23,187
<i>Um…</i>

146
00:09:23,938 --> 00:09:25,189
<i>Then let's just meet at night.</i>

147
00:09:26,023 --> 00:09:27,275
<i>I can't either.</i>

148
00:09:28,025 --> 00:09:30,111
<i>Angelo and I made plans.</i>

149
00:09:30,820 --> 00:09:32,154
<i>What if…</i>

150
00:09:32,238 --> 00:09:34,907
<i>we celebrate</i>
<i>your birthday as it hits midnight?</i>

151
00:09:34,991 --> 00:09:36,659
<i>Just a few hours. Come on.</i>

152
00:09:36,742 --> 00:09:37,618
<i>Please.</i>

153
00:09:38,077 --> 00:09:39,537
<i>I still can't.</i>

154
00:09:40,121 --> 00:09:43,165
<i>When there's a charity event,</i>

155
00:09:43,249 --> 00:09:46,168
<i>we start packing donations at night.</i>

156
00:09:46,877 --> 00:09:51,090
<i>And I'm sure my dad</i>
<i>will keep an eye on me.</i>

157
00:09:53,926 --> 00:09:56,304
<i>Hey, I'm sorry.</i>

158
00:09:56,387 --> 00:09:58,180
[soft music playing]

159
00:09:58,264 --> 00:10:01,225
<i>You know that Angelo and I have always</i>

160
00:10:01,309 --> 00:10:03,102
<i>celebrated my birthday together.</i>

161
00:10:03,811 --> 00:10:07,148
<i>We've been friends</i>
<i>for a long time, remember?</i>

162
00:10:07,857 --> 00:10:11,360
<i>So, he expects nothing will change.</i>

163
00:10:13,154 --> 00:10:16,032
<i>Especially now that we're together.</i>

164
00:10:19,493 --> 00:10:21,537
<i>I know, and I get it.</i>

165
00:10:22,955 --> 00:10:24,999
<i>But of course, it still pains me</i>

166
00:10:25,082 --> 00:10:28,169
<i>that we can't</i>
<i>celebrate your birthday together.</i>

167
00:10:29,045 --> 00:10:30,129
[young Angelo] <i>Well, partner?</i>

168
00:10:30,212 --> 00:10:33,424
<i>Are you bragging to Louisa</i>
<i>about your handsome boyfriend again?</i>

169
00:10:33,507 --> 00:10:36,802
[soft music continues]

170
00:10:38,679 --> 00:10:40,473
<i>Only she will see us.</i>

171
00:10:40,556 --> 00:10:42,350
<i>I'm sure she won't mind.</i>

172
00:10:42,808 --> 00:10:44,644
<i>Besides, Louisa already</i>
<i>knows that we're together.</i>

173
00:10:45,311 --> 00:10:46,646
<i>We're friends.</i>

174
00:10:47,438 --> 00:10:48,397
<i>Right, Louisa?</i>

175
00:10:49,398 --> 00:10:50,483
[Louisa] <i>Hey.</i>

176
00:10:50,566 --> 00:10:52,777
<i>Even though we're friends,</i>
<i>it's still annoying.</i>

177
00:10:52,860 --> 00:10:53,986
[chuckles]

178
00:10:54,070 --> 00:10:55,446
<i>Don't do that in front of me.</i>

179
00:10:57,198 --> 00:10:58,866
<i>What do you want, partner? Coffee?</i>

180
00:10:59,408 --> 00:11:00,409
<i>Or me?</i>

181
00:11:01,452 --> 00:11:02,495
[phone chimes]

182
00:11:02,578 --> 00:11:08,459
[soft music continues]

183
00:11:17,676 --> 00:11:19,512
<i>"AS LONG AS I KNOW I'M THE ONE YOU LOVE,</i>

184
00:11:19,595 --> 00:11:20,930
<i>IT FEELS LIKE WE'RE TOGETHER</i>
<i>ON YOUR BIRTHDAY.</i>

185
00:11:21,013 --> 00:11:22,056
<i>HAPPY BIRTHDAY, BANA!"</i>

186
00:11:22,139 --> 00:11:24,016
[Louisa] <i>As long as</i>
<i>I know I'm the one you love,</i>

187
00:11:24,892 --> 00:11:27,436
<i>it feels like we're together</i>
<i>on your birthday.</i>

188
00:11:29,188 --> 00:11:30,481
<i>Happy birthday, Bana!</i>

189
00:11:30,564 --> 00:11:32,691
[music fades]

190
00:11:33,526 --> 00:11:35,820
<i>How do we do this? It's so hard.</i>

191
00:11:35,903 --> 00:11:37,571
[playful instrumental of
"Sabay Sabay Tayo" playing]

192
00:11:37,655 --> 00:11:39,448
<i>Let me see. I'll check.</i>

193
00:11:41,826 --> 00:11:42,868
<i>Is this it?</i>

194
00:11:42,952 --> 00:11:44,412
<i>Alright. Leave this to me.</i>

195
00:11:44,495 --> 00:11:46,080
<i>Work on the other ones.</i>
<i>I'll take care of this.</i>

196
00:11:46,163 --> 00:11:47,957
<i>- I also need help with mine.</i>
<i>- It's so easy.</i>

197
00:11:48,040 --> 00:11:49,500
<i>I'll help you later after I finish this.</i>

198
00:11:49,583 --> 00:11:50,626
[chuckles]

199
00:11:50,709 --> 00:11:52,503
<i>This is why I want to take up journalism.</i>

200
00:11:52,586 --> 00:11:54,130
<i>- Not much math involved.</i>
- [chuckles]

201
00:11:54,213 --> 00:11:55,339
<i>Oh!</i>

202
00:11:55,423 --> 00:11:56,841
<i>Guys.</i>

203
00:11:56,924 --> 00:11:58,134
<i>Let's go to Longos later.</i>

204
00:11:58,217 --> 00:11:59,427
<i>I heard there's a carnival.</i>

205
00:11:59,510 --> 00:12:00,386
<i>Come on, let's go.</i>

206
00:12:00,469 --> 00:12:03,013
[playful instrumental of
"Sabay Sabay Tayo" continues]

207
00:12:03,097 --> 00:12:05,891
<i>I told my dad I'd be home by 4PM.</i>

208
00:12:06,767 --> 00:12:08,519
<i>You know how he is.</i>

209
00:12:10,187 --> 00:12:13,149
<i>I have to look after our store later.</i>

210
00:12:14,442 --> 00:12:15,734
<i>Sorry.</i>

211
00:12:15,818 --> 00:12:19,822
<i>I told my mom I'd be home before 5PM.</i>

212
00:12:22,158 --> 00:12:23,159
<i>I'd have to pass, too.</i>

213
00:12:23,951 --> 00:12:26,829
<i>Today's the deadline for the article</i>
<i>I'm writing for the school paper.</i>

214
00:12:26,912 --> 00:12:28,122
<i>I have to submit it.</i>

215
00:12:28,747 --> 00:12:30,040
- [clicks mouth]
- [pen clatters]

216
00:12:30,124 --> 00:12:31,208
<i>You're so lame!</i>

217
00:12:32,084 --> 00:12:33,961
<i>What if, just for one day,</i>

218
00:12:34,044 --> 00:12:36,130
<i>you stop being scared of your parents</i>

219
00:12:36,213 --> 00:12:38,257
<i>and just ignore your deadlines?</i>

220
00:12:38,340 --> 00:12:40,092
<i>Come on! Don't be lame!</i>

221
00:12:40,176 --> 00:12:43,053
<i>- Let's have fun just for today.</i>
- [sighs deeply]

222
00:12:45,014 --> 00:12:46,348
<i>Why are you acting like that?</i>

223
00:12:46,974 --> 00:12:48,142
<i>Is there something going on?</i>

224
00:12:48,225 --> 00:12:49,477
<i>What is it?</i>

225
00:12:49,560 --> 00:12:50,519
[scoffs]

226
00:12:51,562 --> 00:12:52,938
<i>Nothing.</i>

227
00:12:54,064 --> 00:12:56,567
<i>What's wrong with</i>
<i>wanting to have fun with my friends?</i>

228
00:12:56,650 --> 00:12:58,402
[soft instrumental of
"Sabay Sabay Tayo" playing]

229
00:12:58,486 --> 00:13:01,030
<i>What are these bracelets for, then? Right?</i>

230
00:13:02,031 --> 00:13:03,199
<i>Come on!</i>

231
00:13:03,782 --> 00:13:05,409
<i>Indulge me just this once. </i>[sighs deeply]

232
00:13:05,493 --> 00:13:06,327
<i>Please.</i>

233
00:13:06,410 --> 00:13:07,620
<i>Hey. Come on.</i>

234
00:13:07,703 --> 00:13:09,497
<i>I guess my mom wouldn't mind.</i>

235
00:13:09,580 --> 00:13:11,373
<i>Great! I knew you'd say yes.</i>

236
00:13:11,457 --> 00:13:12,541
[chuckles]

237
00:13:12,625 --> 00:13:14,502
<i>What reason can I tell my dad?</i>

238
00:13:14,585 --> 00:13:16,587
<i>Nice! Help her think of a reason.</i>

239
00:13:16,670 --> 00:13:18,923
<i>- Okay, later.</i>
- [chuckling]

240
00:13:19,965 --> 00:13:20,841
[phone chimes]

241
00:13:20,925 --> 00:13:22,551
- [Mel] <i>Did you solve it?</i>
- [Alice] <i>Yes.</i>

242
00:13:22,635 --> 00:13:25,346
<i>- "LET'S MEET? I WANT TO BE</i>
<i>- All done.</i>

243
00:13:25,429 --> 00:13:26,722
<i>- WITH YOU ON MY BIRTHDAY."</i>
<i>- See?</i>

244
00:13:26,805 --> 00:13:29,642
<i>Oh, guys. I'll get going now. </i>[chuckles]

245
00:13:29,725 --> 00:13:30,768
<i>- Huh?</i>
<i>- What?</i>

246
00:13:30,851 --> 00:13:32,269
<i>Didn't you just invite us?</i>

247
00:13:33,062 --> 00:13:34,438
<i>We can reschedule it.</i>

248
00:13:34,522 --> 00:13:37,149
<i>Yes! Let's have fun next time. </i>[chuckles]

249
00:13:37,233 --> 00:13:38,734
<i>- Okay. Bye!</i>
<i>- Hey.</i>

250
00:13:38,817 --> 00:13:40,528
<i>You're going to him, aren't you?</i>

251
00:13:40,611 --> 00:13:43,155
<i>You're leaving us for your lover?</i>

252
00:13:43,239 --> 00:13:44,323
<i>Traitor!</i>

253
00:13:45,616 --> 00:13:47,409
<i>- Don't be so grumpy.</i>
<i>- The nerve.</i>

254
00:13:47,493 --> 00:13:48,911
<i>We'll hang out next time, really!</i>

255
00:13:48,994 --> 00:13:50,329
<i>- No, don't bother.</i>
<i>- Next time!</i>

256
00:13:50,412 --> 00:13:52,331
<i>- No!</i>
<i>- Okay, bye!</i>

257
00:13:55,793 --> 00:13:57,545
<i>Liezel?</i> [chuckles]

258
00:14:02,132 --> 00:14:03,509
<i>Happy birthday!</i>

259
00:14:03,592 --> 00:14:04,510
<i>Thank you.</i>

260
00:14:05,052 --> 00:14:06,720
<i>What about your dad? The charity?</i>

261
00:14:06,804 --> 00:14:08,305
<i>I pretended to be sick.</i>

262
00:14:09,014 --> 00:14:10,766
<i>Him and Mama went to the event.</i>

263
00:14:10,849 --> 00:14:12,601
<i>I was left alone at home.</i>

264
00:14:12,685 --> 00:14:15,271
<i>I just need to get back</i>
<i>before they come home.</i>

265
00:14:18,566 --> 00:14:19,775
<i>It's okay.</i>

266
00:14:21,694 --> 00:14:24,154
<i>Even a few hours is</i>
<i>fine as long as you're here.</i>

267
00:14:24,238 --> 00:14:29,076
["Nagmamahal Lang Ako"
by KZ Tandingan playing]

268
00:14:40,129 --> 00:14:41,630
[giggling]

269
00:14:44,383 --> 00:14:45,384
<i>Whoo!</i>

270
00:14:45,467 --> 00:14:47,386
[laughing]

271
00:14:52,600 --> 00:14:54,101
<i>Are you having fun?</i>

272
00:14:57,479 --> 00:14:58,647
[clears throat]

273
00:15:00,691 --> 00:15:01,901
<i>Let's leave.</i>

274
00:15:02,735 --> 00:15:05,195
<i>Huh? How long have we been here?</i>

275
00:15:05,821 --> 00:15:06,822
<i>No. I meant…</i>

276
00:15:09,033 --> 00:15:11,619
<i>Let's leave Amurao after we graduate.</i>

277
00:15:13,287 --> 00:15:15,039
<i>Let's move somewhere far away.</i>

278
00:15:17,166 --> 00:15:20,920
<i>Somewhere we don't have</i>
<i>to worry about being caught by your dad.</i>

279
00:15:23,839 --> 00:15:25,299
<i>We're leaving?</i>

280
00:15:27,718 --> 00:15:29,553
<i>I know it won't be easy.</i>

281
00:15:30,346 --> 00:15:32,431
<i>But we'll have each other.</i>

282
00:15:33,557 --> 00:15:35,100
<i>Where will we go?</i>

283
00:15:35,809 --> 00:15:38,562
<i>What about college?</i>
<i>How will we make a living?</i>

284
00:15:38,646 --> 00:15:40,397
<i>We'll look for jobs.</i>

285
00:15:40,481 --> 00:15:43,025
<i>We'll share the burden. We can do it.</i>

286
00:15:43,108 --> 00:15:47,029
<i>As long as we're together,</i>
<i>I'm sure we can face anything.</i>

287
00:15:47,112 --> 00:15:50,991
["Nagmamahal Lang Ako" continues]

288
00:15:51,075 --> 00:15:52,409
<i>Are you in?</i>

289
00:15:55,746 --> 00:15:58,248
<i>Yes, I'm in.</i>

290
00:16:00,918 --> 00:16:02,419
[exhales]

291
00:16:06,382 --> 00:16:08,425
[Louisa]<i> We need to save</i>
<i>some money before we graduate.</i>

292
00:16:08,509 --> 00:16:10,469
<i>- So we'll have savings when we leave.</i>
- [song fades]

293
00:16:11,053 --> 00:16:14,348
<i>I'll convince Papa</i>
<i>to let me get a part-time job.</i>

294
00:16:20,187 --> 00:16:21,397
<i>You know…</i>

295
00:16:22,856 --> 00:16:25,567
<i>I still can't believe</i>
<i>that you're really coming with me.</i>

296
00:16:28,904 --> 00:16:30,531
<i>For the first time,</i>

297
00:16:30,614 --> 00:16:33,993
<i>I'm excited about</i>
<i>what my future will bring.</i>

298
00:16:35,953 --> 00:16:39,289
<i>Before, I knew what</i>
<i>my life was going to be.</i>

299
00:16:40,040 --> 00:16:42,042
<i>I'll attend college here.</i>

300
00:16:42,960 --> 00:16:44,628
<i>After graduating…</i>

301
00:16:45,546 --> 00:16:47,506
<i>I'm supposed to marry Angelo.</i>

302
00:16:48,507 --> 00:16:50,634
<i>Because that's what Papa wants.</i>

303
00:16:51,719 --> 00:16:53,220
<i>I feel like…</i>

304
00:16:54,638 --> 00:16:57,474
<i>I only became</i>
<i>Angelo's girlfriend in high school</i>

305
00:16:57,558 --> 00:16:59,435
<i>just to get one over Papa.</i>

306
00:17:02,021 --> 00:17:03,147
<i>Pathetic, right?</i>

307
00:17:03,230 --> 00:17:07,192
[insects chirping]

308
00:17:07,276 --> 00:17:08,485
<i>That's not true.</i>

309
00:17:09,194 --> 00:17:10,738
<i>You impress me.</i>

310
00:17:12,281 --> 00:17:14,533
<i>Because you didn't turn out like your dad.</i>

311
00:17:15,617 --> 00:17:17,619
<i>You're still a good person.</i>

312
00:17:20,372 --> 00:17:21,749
<i>You're a good person too.</i>

313
00:17:21,832 --> 00:17:23,834
<i>Even after what happened to your parents.</i>

314
00:17:25,794 --> 00:17:28,672
<i>If only I could tell them</i>

315
00:17:28,756 --> 00:17:31,341
<i>that you're the best</i>
<i>person I have ever met,</i>

316
00:17:32,092 --> 00:17:33,385
<i>I would have done it already.</i>

317
00:17:34,511 --> 00:17:38,640
<i>I'd prefer that instead of letting them</i>
<i>think bad things about you.</i>

318
00:17:44,855 --> 00:17:47,441
<i>I don't care about their opinions.</i>

319
00:17:47,524 --> 00:17:49,860
<i>I only care about yours.</i>

320
00:17:53,489 --> 00:17:54,865
<i>I love you, Liezel.</i>

321
00:17:55,407 --> 00:17:56,700
<i>I love you.</i>

322
00:17:57,284 --> 00:17:58,702
<i>Together forever?</i>

323
00:18:03,040 --> 00:18:04,458
<i>Forever.</i>

324
00:18:05,918 --> 00:18:11,131
["Nagmamahal Lang Ako"
by KZ Tandingan playing]

325
00:18:31,193 --> 00:18:33,904
- [sobs]
- [song fades]

326
00:18:33,987 --> 00:18:35,405
Forever…

327
00:18:36,532 --> 00:18:38,450
[somber music playing]

328
00:18:38,534 --> 00:18:42,037
So, Louisa was going to leave with you?

329
00:18:45,707 --> 00:18:47,584
[sniffles, exhales]

330
00:18:49,211 --> 00:18:50,504
We planned it all.

331
00:18:52,464 --> 00:18:55,634
After graduation,
we were supposed to leave together.

332
00:18:56,093 --> 00:18:59,012
But Papa had other plans
for me back then. [sobs]

333
00:19:01,765 --> 00:19:03,267
He suddenly told me that…

334
00:19:04,059 --> 00:19:06,353
That he was going to send me to Bicol.

335
00:19:07,187 --> 00:19:09,064
[sniffles]

336
00:19:09,148 --> 00:19:11,275
He said I was going
to take care of a sick aunt.

337
00:19:12,317 --> 00:19:15,070
He said I needed to leave
before the graduation ceremony.

338
00:19:18,323 --> 00:19:20,951
So Louisa and
I changed our plans after that.

339
00:19:22,077 --> 00:19:23,620
We decided that…

340
00:19:25,455 --> 00:19:28,667
That we should leave before that happens.

341
00:19:30,544 --> 00:19:32,421
We were supposed to leave,

342
00:19:33,338 --> 00:19:35,132
after your birthday.

343
00:19:35,215 --> 00:19:37,467
[shaky exhale]

344
00:19:37,551 --> 00:19:42,764
[pensive music playing]

345
00:19:53,859 --> 00:19:56,195
[music fades]

346
00:20:05,579 --> 00:20:06,663
[exhales]

347
00:20:26,225 --> 00:20:27,392
[exhales]

348
00:20:28,644 --> 00:20:34,483
<i>"AFTER WE VISIT ERICA, LET'S LEAVE.</i>

349
00:20:35,400 --> 00:20:37,903
<i>ARE YOU READY?"</i>

350
00:20:39,238 --> 00:20:40,280
[phone chimes]

351
00:20:40,364 --> 00:20:45,869
[gentle music playing]

352
00:20:47,287 --> 00:20:51,959
<i>"I'M EXCITED, BUT STILL A BIT SCARED."</i>

353
00:20:52,459 --> 00:20:53,669
[phone chimes]

354
00:20:53,752 --> 00:20:59,508
<i>"DON'T WORRY.</i>
<i>JUST THINK OF US BEING TOGETHER FOREVER."</i>

355
00:21:00,842 --> 00:21:04,805
<i>"FOREVER!"</i>

356
00:21:04,888 --> 00:21:06,181
[phone chimes]

357
00:21:09,059 --> 00:21:10,852
<i>"FOREVER!"</i>

358
00:21:16,233 --> 00:21:17,985
[music fades]

359
00:21:18,068 --> 00:21:19,361
[Samuel] <i>Who's that? Is that Louisa?</i>

360
00:21:21,071 --> 00:21:22,739
<i>Ah, yes, Papa.</i>

361
00:21:22,823 --> 00:21:25,659
<i>She couldn't contact Angelo.</i>

362
00:21:25,742 --> 00:21:27,327
<i>She wanted to ask him something.</i>

363
00:21:27,411 --> 00:21:29,538
<i>They work at the coffee shop, remember?</i>

364
00:21:29,621 --> 00:21:31,581
<i>Stop lying.</i>

365
00:21:32,165 --> 00:21:34,084
<i>I know what the two of you are doing.</i>

366
00:21:36,086 --> 00:21:38,755
<i>Huh? I don't know</i>
<i>what you're talking about.</i>

367
00:21:38,839 --> 00:21:40,132
<i>You are a sinner!</i>

368
00:21:40,924 --> 00:21:42,801
<i>I know your secret!</i>

369
00:21:42,884 --> 00:21:45,095
<i>You can't fool me anymore!</i>

370
00:21:45,178 --> 00:21:49,558
[tense music playing]

371
00:21:52,894 --> 00:21:54,521
<i>Someone might see us!</i>

372
00:21:54,604 --> 00:21:57,441
<i>Yeah, but no one will recognize us here.</i>

373
00:21:57,524 --> 00:21:59,568
<i>We're at the next town.</i>

374
00:22:03,113 --> 00:22:06,450
[giggling]

375
00:22:08,368 --> 00:22:09,995
[Louisa] <i>What about this ride?</i>
<i>Can you handle this?</i>

376
00:22:10,078 --> 00:22:11,079
[camera shutter clicks]

377
00:22:11,163 --> 00:22:12,998
[Liezel] <i>No, I don't think I can.</i>

378
00:22:16,877 --> 00:22:20,213
<i>Pastor Samuel, I'm sending you a picture.</i>

379
00:22:20,297 --> 00:22:23,175
<i>Your daughter's doing something sinful.</i>

380
00:22:24,051 --> 00:22:28,263
<i>Thankfully, that woman</i>
<i>was loyal to our church and to me.</i>

381
00:22:29,639 --> 00:22:34,019
<i>I convinced her to not tell</i>
<i>anyone else about what she saw.</i>

382
00:22:35,020 --> 00:22:37,939
<i>Because if she did, I would be humiliated!</i>

383
00:22:38,023 --> 00:22:39,816
<i>And it would have been because of you!</i>

384
00:22:39,900 --> 00:22:42,194
[tense music continues]

385
00:22:42,277 --> 00:22:43,653
<i>How could you do this?</i>

386
00:22:44,905 --> 00:22:51,453
<i>Your whole life,</i>
<i>I taught you to be righteous and clean!</i>

387
00:22:51,912 --> 00:22:55,916
<i>I raised you to hold close</i>
<i>to your heart the teachings of God!</i>

388
00:22:55,999 --> 00:23:00,295
<i>But you let the poison</i>
<i>of that girl cloud your mind.</i>

389
00:23:00,378 --> 00:23:02,005
<i>A girl, Liezel.</i>

390
00:23:03,131 --> 00:23:04,716
<i>A girl like you.</i>

391
00:23:04,800 --> 00:23:09,930
<i>I thought that this girl</i>
<i>only destroyed the lives of boys.</i>

392
00:23:10,597 --> 00:23:12,641
<i>Turns out, she goes after girls also.</i>

393
00:23:13,308 --> 00:23:14,559
<i>And she went after my daughter!</i>

394
00:23:15,060 --> 00:23:16,853
<i>You're my daughter, Liezel,</i>

395
00:23:17,437 --> 00:23:20,273
<i>but you succumbed</i>
<i>to temptation so quickly!</i>

396
00:23:20,357 --> 00:23:22,109
<i>You are too weak!</i>

397
00:23:22,692 --> 00:23:26,071
<i>Is this why you want to send me to Bicol?</i>

398
00:23:26,154 --> 00:23:29,032
<i>Yes! To get you as far</i>
<i>away as possible from her.</i>

399
00:23:29,616 --> 00:23:32,953
<i>You will forget about her. She is sinful!</i>

400
00:23:33,036 --> 00:23:35,872
<i>She's poison! Like Eve was to Adam!</i>

401
00:23:35,956 --> 00:23:37,916
<i>- She's not like that!</i>
<i>- What?!</i>

402
00:23:37,999 --> 00:23:39,668
<i>Louisa's not poison!</i>

403
00:23:40,293 --> 00:23:43,338
<i>She's the kindest person I ever met!</i>

404
00:23:43,421 --> 00:23:45,549
<i>She loves me, and I love her!</i>

405
00:23:45,632 --> 00:23:47,050
<i>And there is nothing wrong in that!</i>

406
00:23:47,634 --> 00:23:48,510
[smacks]

407
00:23:48,593 --> 00:23:49,719
<i>Samuel!</i>

408
00:23:50,345 --> 00:23:51,847
<i>All of that is wrong!</i>

409
00:23:51,930 --> 00:23:56,518
<i>But you can't see</i>
<i>it because she has poisoned your mind!</i>

410
00:23:56,601 --> 00:24:01,022
[tense music continues]

411
00:24:04,901 --> 00:24:06,027
<i>What are you doing?</i>

412
00:24:06,111 --> 00:24:07,654
<i>- What are you doing?!</i>
<i>- I'm leaving.</i>

413
00:24:07,737 --> 00:24:09,156
<i>I'm leaving!</i>

414
00:24:09,239 --> 00:24:10,365
<i>To be with that girl?</i>

415
00:24:10,448 --> 00:24:11,908
<i>You can't stop me.</i>

416
00:24:12,742 --> 00:24:13,827
<i>You're not leaving!</i>

417
00:24:14,953 --> 00:24:18,623
<i>Go on!</i>
<i>Let our church members see the truth!</i>

418
00:24:21,376 --> 00:24:22,586
<i>That girl…</i>

419
00:24:23,253 --> 00:24:24,504
<i>I can hurt her.</i>

420
00:24:26,381 --> 00:24:28,175
<i>I'll have her arrested.</i>

421
00:24:28,258 --> 00:24:30,677
<i>I'll say that she robbed us.</i>

422
00:24:31,511 --> 00:24:35,724
<i>And I'm sure that they'll believe me.</i>

423
00:24:35,807 --> 00:24:37,684
<i>I'll file a complaint against her!</i>

424
00:24:37,767 --> 00:24:39,686
<i>She'll rot in prison!</i>

425
00:24:40,437 --> 00:24:41,897
<i>You can't do that.</i>

426
00:24:41,980 --> 00:24:43,106
<i>I'll do it!</i>

427
00:24:43,190 --> 00:24:45,775
<i>You call me sinful…</i>

428
00:24:46,818 --> 00:24:48,236
<i>What about you?!</i>

429
00:24:48,320 --> 00:24:50,614
<i>The Lord will forgive me.</i>

430
00:24:51,156 --> 00:24:54,284
<i>I'm only doing this for your sake!</i>

431
00:24:54,910 --> 00:24:57,287
<i>Is it really for my sake, or yours?!</i>

432
00:24:57,746 --> 00:24:59,164
<i>You're a selfish man!</i>

433
00:25:01,833 --> 00:25:02,876
<i>Ma…</i>

434
00:25:02,959 --> 00:25:04,794
<i>If you go with that girl…</i>

435
00:25:06,129 --> 00:25:07,756
<i>I'll ruin her.</i>

436
00:25:08,757 --> 00:25:10,759
<i>I'll ruin her life.</i>

437
00:25:10,842 --> 00:25:14,930
<i>Not just here in Amurao,</i>
<i>but anywhere she will ever go!</i>

438
00:25:16,932 --> 00:25:18,767
<i>You know that I will do it.</i>

439
00:25:21,436 --> 00:25:23,396
<i>Is that what you want?</i>

440
00:25:25,106 --> 00:25:26,524
<i>Think about it.</i>

441
00:25:28,151 --> 00:25:31,988
<i>I'm going to leave the door open tonight.</i>

442
00:25:32,072 --> 00:25:35,200
<i>If you want to leave, fine.</i>

443
00:25:35,283 --> 00:25:38,912
<i>But you know what the consequence will be!</i>

444
00:25:38,995 --> 00:25:44,084
[unsettling music playing]

445
00:25:48,463 --> 00:25:52,801
[crying]

446
00:25:59,099 --> 00:26:04,062
[unsettling music continues]

447
00:26:13,655 --> 00:26:15,615
<i>Since when did</i>
<i>you know about Louisa and I?</i>

448
00:26:15,699 --> 00:26:17,367
<i>What you did to me hurt so much.</i>

449
00:26:17,450 --> 00:26:19,536
<i>I thought Louisa was my friend.</i>

450
00:26:19,619 --> 00:26:21,162
<i>I thought you loved me, Liezel.</i>

451
00:26:21,246 --> 00:26:22,455
<i>But with Louisa, you act differently.</i>

452
00:26:22,539 --> 00:26:23,832
<i>The way you smile around her…</i>

453
00:26:23,915 --> 00:26:26,835
<i>I've never seen</i>
<i>you smile the same way to me.</i>

454
00:26:26,918 --> 00:26:30,046
<i>I thought I could lie to myself.</i>

455
00:26:30,130 --> 00:26:31,881
<i>I don't want to think</i>
<i>about or remember that night.</i>

456
